WEBVTT

00:12.140 --> 00:16.840
[August 17, 2012]

00:31.350 --> 00:31.920
Move!

00:46.750 --> 00:47.610
Take them away!

00:48.280 --> 00:49.070
Anyone else here?

00:49.070 --> 00:50.560
Bring all detainees to the vehicle.

00:50.560 --> 00:51.070
Report!

00:51.090 --> 00:52.860
Armed drug dealers spotted
in the northwest corner.

00:52.860 --> 00:53.990
Requesting backup.

01:09.200 --> 01:09.710
Talk.

01:10.430 --> 01:12.289
Are you hiding something from me?

01:35.370 --> 01:36.620
You're Zhou Chuan.

01:37.550 --> 01:38.620
Who are you?

01:39.340 --> 01:40.940
I have no grudge against you.

01:41.000 --> 01:42.400
I didn't want to kill you,

01:42.680 --> 01:44.210
but someone wants you dead.

01:47.440 --> 01:48.110
Come on out.

01:48.560 --> 01:49.620
Verify the target.

01:53.770 --> 01:57.130
[Zhou Chuan, Vice Captain, SWAT team
of Haizhou Public Security Bureau]

01:57.700 --> 02:00.470
[8.17 Case]

03:18.930 --> 03:24.690
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:25.000 --> 03:27.410
[Episode 1]

03:44.630 --> 03:48.150
[Zhou Jin, Officer, Security Management
Brigade of Nancheng Branch, Haizhou City]

03:56.030 --> 03:56.680
Brother.

03:57.680 --> 03:58.790
I just hope that

03:59.310 --> 04:01.560
my future life would be smooth and easy,

04:01.840 --> 04:03.730
like a straight river,

04:04.120 --> 04:05.540
without wind or waves.

04:05.940 --> 04:08.060
Only smooth sailing.

04:09.120 --> 04:11.120
Life is supposed to be difficult.

04:12.030 --> 04:13.890
Nothing is certain in this world.

04:14.360 --> 04:15.420
Live in the moment.

04:16.070 --> 04:17.560
The feelings you have right now

04:17.560 --> 04:18.760
are what matter most.

04:19.839 --> 04:21.430
Alright, stop overthinking.

04:21.430 --> 04:22.760
I'll always be here for you.

04:22.760 --> 04:23.880
Awesome!

04:32.880 --> 04:33.800
Zhou Chuan.

04:34.630 --> 04:35.950
He was the top sniper

04:36.110 --> 04:38.260
of Haizhou City's SWAT team.

04:38.960 --> 04:41.170
He died in the line of duty
during the 8.17 Case.

04:41.170 --> 04:44.900
[Jiang Hansheng, Researcher, Criminal Research
Office, Binjiang Province Public Security]

04:41.240 --> 04:44.159
His Type 92 service pistol and the killer

04:44.510 --> 04:45.630
are both missing.

04:46.120 --> 04:47.880
At the scene, he was shot twice.

04:46.880 --> 04:52.500
[Personal Information: Zhou Chuan]

04:48.750 --> 04:50.720
One bullet hit his calf,

04:51.040 --> 04:52.430
immobilizing him.

04:53.680 --> 04:55.070
Another bullet hit the back of his head

04:55.070 --> 04:56.270
at a 45-degree angle,

04:56.360 --> 04:57.430
from top to bottom.

04:58.000 --> 05:00.250
His abdomen was stabbed
more than 10 times.

05:00.250 --> 05:01.980
Even without those 2 gunshots,

05:02.290 --> 05:03.950
he would have died on the spot.

05:24.620 --> 05:25.130
Come in.

05:27.680 --> 05:28.340
Professor.

05:29.000 --> 05:30.480
The comparison results are in.

05:30.480 --> 05:31.390
The DNA of the perpetrator

05:31.390 --> 05:33.050
found on Zhou Chuan's clothes

05:33.190 --> 05:35.060
matches perfectly with the DNA

05:34.230 --> 05:37.420
[Wang Pengze, Director, Criminal Research
Office, Binjiang Province Public Security]

05:35.080 --> 05:36.070
from the 1997 Huaiguang Case.

05:36.070 --> 05:37.270
It's the same person.

05:37.310 --> 05:39.710
We can investigate the cases together now.

05:42.670 --> 05:44.670
I know what you're concerned about.

05:45.600 --> 05:46.530
Jiang Hansheng.

05:47.580 --> 05:49.900
I haven't agreed to let you

05:50.000 --> 05:51.600
resume investigation work.

05:51.950 --> 05:53.409
This is not your business.

05:53.800 --> 05:54.800
You can leave now.

05:54.800 --> 05:56.200
Close the door after you.

05:56.500 --> 05:58.090
I will submit an appeal in my own name

05:58.090 --> 05:59.870
to the Provincial High Procuratorate

05:59.870 --> 06:02.800
to request a reinvestigation
of the Huaiguang case.

06:07.040 --> 06:07.970
Jiang Hansheng.

06:09.100 --> 06:11.060
Am I speaking in a foreign language?

06:11.060 --> 06:13.190
Don't you understand what I'm saying?

06:13.580 --> 06:16.310
This is not the time for you to show off.

06:18.310 --> 06:18.970
Professor.

06:20.240 --> 06:21.700
I'm not trying to show off.

06:22.750 --> 06:24.200
Since it's the same person,

06:24.200 --> 06:25.950
the profile from the Huaiguang Case

06:25.950 --> 06:27.630
also applies to the 8.17 Case.

06:28.510 --> 06:30.270
The killer has long lacked affection,

06:30.270 --> 06:31.430
so he could have easily developed

06:31.430 --> 06:33.430
histrionic personality disorder.

06:34.040 --> 06:35.190
If I were him,

06:35.680 --> 06:37.560
I would definitely use various channels

06:37.560 --> 06:39.220
to monitor police movements.

06:39.830 --> 06:40.630
If necessary,

06:41.240 --> 06:43.640
I would even give an irrelevant testimony.

06:43.800 --> 06:44.560
This way,

06:44.800 --> 06:46.360
I could observe these fools

06:46.360 --> 06:48.630
I've been playing with up close.

06:49.830 --> 06:50.870
So I want to appear

06:50.870 --> 06:52.070
on a legal TV program.

06:55.800 --> 06:58.480
Are you planning to challenge

07:00.040 --> 07:01.750
the murderer on television?

07:05.160 --> 07:07.520
Welcome to Legal Knowledge in Action.

07:07.650 --> 07:09.510
Today we have invited

07:09.510 --> 07:12.160
a young expert in criminal psychology,

07:12.180 --> 07:13.040
Officer Jiang.

07:13.600 --> 07:16.040
Officer Jiang will use real cases

07:16.160 --> 07:18.020
to discuss psychology with us...

07:20.220 --> 07:23.720
[2017]

07:24.790 --> 07:28.180
[Haizhou City]

07:29.960 --> 07:33.370
[Zhou Jin and Jiang Hansheng's first date]

07:31.100 --> 07:33.159
It's not that you're not good enough;

07:33.800 --> 07:36.190
it's just that I'm not keen
on dating right now.

07:36.190 --> 07:37.510
You just don't want to date me.

07:37.510 --> 07:38.120
No.

07:38.120 --> 07:39.270
I want to focus on my work.

07:39.270 --> 07:40.750
So you'd rather work than date me.

07:40.750 --> 07:41.390
No.

07:42.390 --> 07:43.240
Because I know

07:43.240 --> 07:44.710
you're looking for marriage.

07:44.710 --> 07:47.040
So I need to think this through carefully.

07:47.070 --> 07:48.630
Think carefully about how to reject me.

07:48.630 --> 07:49.190
No.

07:49.870 --> 07:51.080
You shouldn't interpret it that way.

07:51.080 --> 07:52.110
You're such a good catch.

07:52.110 --> 07:53.720
There must be many girls
who would like you.

07:53.720 --> 07:54.770
Just not you.

07:55.650 --> 07:56.730
We can be friends.

07:57.750 --> 07:59.409
At most, I'm your backup plan.

08:01.250 --> 08:02.510
What's wrong with you?

08:03.010 --> 08:05.070
I answered your questions properly.

08:05.370 --> 08:06.000
Why did you twist

08:06.000 --> 08:07.160
everything I say?

08:08.070 --> 08:08.680
I'm sorry.

08:10.350 --> 08:12.210
I shouldn't have said it out loud.

08:12.350 --> 08:14.000
Shouldn't have said it out loud?

08:14.000 --> 08:16.260
No, you shouldn't have thought that way.

08:17.950 --> 08:21.270
It's just that everything you've said
matches the "heartless girl" quotebook.

08:21.270 --> 08:22.560
What quotebook?

08:23.270 --> 08:25.040
You said you wanted to talk to me.

08:25.040 --> 08:26.870
I had a feeling
you were going to reject me.

08:26.870 --> 08:28.270
So I looked it up online.

08:28.730 --> 08:29.360
I'm sorry.

08:45.090 --> 08:46.400
The one who should be apologizing

08:46.400 --> 08:47.400
is me.

08:48.030 --> 08:49.030
I really

08:49.050 --> 08:50.180
thought I could do this.

08:50.180 --> 08:51.510
I wanted to give it a try.

08:51.720 --> 08:53.320
But after trying, I realized

08:53.480 --> 08:54.390
I couldn't.

08:55.390 --> 08:57.670
Maybe I just don't know
how to date someone anymore.

08:57.670 --> 08:58.270
I'm sorry.

08:59.270 --> 09:00.270
It's all my fault.

09:01.790 --> 09:03.050
Say whatever you want.

09:03.080 --> 09:03.680
It's okay.

09:07.440 --> 09:08.080
Zhou Jin.

09:09.550 --> 09:11.270
It's not that you don't know how to love.

09:11.270 --> 09:12.890
You just don't know
how to handle arranged dates.

09:12.890 --> 09:14.320
A stranger sits in front of you

09:14.320 --> 09:15.910
and says he wants to marry you.

09:15.910 --> 09:17.840
Not only can't you get excited about it,

09:17.840 --> 09:19.370
but you also find it absurd.

09:19.670 --> 09:21.440
You prefer genuine excitement.

09:21.440 --> 09:23.000
You only know how to be passionate,

09:23.000 --> 09:23.870
focused,

09:24.200 --> 09:25.860
and deeply committed in love.

09:26.120 --> 09:27.050
Because you know

09:28.030 --> 09:29.940
what we have isn't love.

09:31.600 --> 09:32.750
Rationally, you think

09:32.750 --> 09:34.510
you should be of the age to get married.

09:34.510 --> 09:36.590
You want to reassure your family,

09:36.910 --> 09:38.790
but you don't know how to skip over love

09:38.790 --> 09:40.240
and go straight to marriage.

09:40.240 --> 09:41.480
So the more we meet,

09:41.510 --> 09:43.170
the more panicked you become.

09:43.390 --> 09:44.440
But I can see that

09:45.240 --> 09:46.120
you're already trying very hard

09:46.120 --> 09:47.780
every time you come to meet me.

09:48.640 --> 09:49.370
Rejecting me

09:50.040 --> 09:52.070
is you respecting your own heart.

09:58.320 --> 09:58.960
I'm sorry.

09:59.790 --> 10:02.050
I shouldn't have analyzed you like this.

10:05.850 --> 10:06.420
Okay.

10:07.620 --> 10:08.420
I understand.

10:10.400 --> 10:11.230
I'll go now.

10:20.140 --> 10:21.070
Jiang Hansheng!

10:22.790 --> 10:24.050
I just said a few words.

10:24.630 --> 10:26.690
You didn't have to jump into the lake.

10:27.820 --> 10:29.220
I forgot we were on a boat.

10:37.500 --> 10:39.700
This paper needs to be spread out to dry.

10:40.100 --> 10:41.230
This is useless now.

10:42.880 --> 10:46.190
30 Reasons Why Jiang Hansheng Is
Perfect for Zhou Jin.

10:48.480 --> 10:50.610
Is this how you pursue girls in general?

10:50.610 --> 10:51.600
I've never pursued a girl before.

10:51.600 --> 10:53.330
So the girls pursued you instead?

10:53.330 --> 10:54.530
I don't believe that.

10:54.720 --> 10:55.950
I've never been in a relationship.

10:55.950 --> 10:56.990
That's impossible.

10:56.990 --> 10:57.590
It's true.

10:58.150 --> 10:59.280
My heart rate is low.

10:59.320 --> 11:01.450
I rarely feel that flutter in my heart.

11:02.000 --> 11:03.130
Do you feel it for me?

11:14.550 --> 11:15.740
Let me take a look.

11:15.920 --> 11:17.250
What did you write here?

11:17.840 --> 11:19.300
Physical compatibility.

11:19.790 --> 11:22.150
Perfect height difference.

11:26.360 --> 11:28.220
Compatible age and zodiac signs.

11:28.230 --> 11:30.230
Compatible fortune and horoscope.

11:30.630 --> 11:32.090
Had genetic testing done.

11:32.210 --> 11:33.060
Good genes.

11:33.590 --> 11:35.920
You've really done your research online.

11:35.950 --> 11:38.210
Attitude: Dating with marriage in mind.

11:38.210 --> 11:40.740
Decision-making: Always prioritizing you.

11:45.520 --> 11:47.050
You value emotions deeply.

11:48.010 --> 11:49.440
You need someone

11:51.050 --> 11:53.510
who takes relationships just as seriously.

11:55.130 --> 11:56.060
I am that person.

12:05.600 --> 12:07.540
I don't have much confidence in dating

12:07.540 --> 12:08.940
because I've failed before.

12:07.640 --> 12:12.970
[Zhou Jin and Jiang Hansheng's second date]

12:09.510 --> 12:10.530
I had

12:10.790 --> 12:12.640
a boyfriend

12:13.510 --> 12:14.870
for many years.

12:15.940 --> 12:17.200
Are you still in touch?

12:24.470 --> 12:26.070
How long have you been apart?

12:27.010 --> 12:27.760
Two years.

12:30.750 --> 12:31.550
Five years.

12:35.520 --> 12:37.250
His name is Jiang Cheng, right?

12:52.290 --> 12:53.220
If you can let go,

12:53.380 --> 12:54.180
then I can too.

13:01.110 --> 13:03.570
[2012]

13:03.590 --> 13:06.000
[Longwan Hotel]

13:06.030 --> 13:11.160
[10 days after the 8.17 operation]

13:12.240 --> 13:13.170
Police! Open up!

13:13.790 --> 13:14.790
Police! Don't move!

13:14.790 --> 13:15.460
Freeze!

13:15.500 --> 13:16.170
Stay still!

13:16.190 --> 13:17.390
Let me explain first.

13:18.150 --> 13:19.100
Put your clothes on.

13:19.100 --> 13:20.160
What's your name?

13:21.990 --> 13:22.830
Jiang Cheng.

13:47.130 --> 13:48.680
Due to the absence

13:48.700 --> 13:50.440
of a father figure in his birth family,

13:50.440 --> 13:52.390
the killer developed extreme insecurity

13:52.390 --> 13:53.990
and a desperate need for love

13:54.260 --> 13:55.120
and attention.

13:55.600 --> 13:56.660
I also believe that

13:57.080 --> 13:58.810
he was abandoned by his mother.

13:59.510 --> 14:01.290
He considers himself an artist,

14:01.290 --> 14:02.660
using an artistic facade

14:02.660 --> 14:03.920
to cover up his crimes.

14:04.510 --> 14:05.630
These victims

14:05.680 --> 14:07.520
are merely substitutes for him.

14:08.390 --> 14:09.150
It's clear

14:09.660 --> 14:10.540
that mentally,

14:10.760 --> 14:12.290
he has experienced trauma.

14:13.700 --> 14:14.500
I believe

14:14.850 --> 14:16.400
defining him as a psychopath

14:16.400 --> 14:17.860
isn't entirely accurate.

14:17.880 --> 14:20.300
However, he does possess
traits of this personality type.

14:20.300 --> 14:22.030
How should we understand this?

14:22.960 --> 14:25.080
In medicine, there is a scale

14:25.080 --> 14:25.970
for assessing psychosis,

14:25.970 --> 14:27.630
called the Hare's Checklist.

14:27.650 --> 14:29.510
It includes 20 assessment items.

14:29.550 --> 14:29.880
For example,

14:29.880 --> 14:31.610
whether they appear charming,

14:31.630 --> 14:33.830
have strong manipulative tendencies,

14:33.880 --> 14:36.030
or have a limit to the range
of emotions they receive,

14:36.030 --> 14:37.510
which is what we commonly call

14:37.510 --> 14:38.640
the lack of empathy.

14:39.480 --> 14:40.120
Also,

14:40.280 --> 14:42.000
if they have
a grandiose sense of self-worth,

14:42.000 --> 14:43.760
are pathological liars,
or have a series of other

14:43.760 --> 14:44.960
personality traits.

14:45.260 --> 14:46.330
I believe that

14:46.360 --> 14:47.960
if the Red Dress serial killer

14:47.960 --> 14:49.620
were to take this assessment,

14:49.640 --> 14:51.480
he would score high in many areas.

14:51.480 --> 14:52.610
But there's one item

14:52.840 --> 14:53.960
that he would score low on.

14:53.960 --> 14:54.960
Which one?

14:56.030 --> 14:57.640
Limited emotional range.

14:58.260 --> 14:59.720
Because, on the contrary,

14:59.760 --> 15:01.220
his emotions are intense.

15:01.260 --> 15:02.190
Strong emotions

15:02.290 --> 15:02.960
are what drove him to kill

15:02.960 --> 15:04.810
and stage the crime scenes.

15:05.460 --> 15:07.970
From how meticulously
he planned the murders,

15:07.970 --> 15:09.420
he appears to be calm

15:09.440 --> 15:10.500
and cold-blooded.

15:10.580 --> 15:12.640
But the drive behind his violent acts

15:13.030 --> 15:14.640
comes from being triggered.

15:15.000 --> 15:16.360
Because deep inside,

15:16.670 --> 15:19.000
he's still a child with emotional trauma.

15:40.640 --> 15:41.700
They took the bait.

15:45.240 --> 15:46.570
Keep a close eye on them.

15:56.580 --> 15:57.240
Don't move.

15:58.320 --> 15:59.720
Move, and I'll shoot you.

16:02.800 --> 16:03.530
Let me go!

16:28.440 --> 16:29.570
Tie his hands.

16:35.640 --> 16:36.360
Tie him up.

16:41.530 --> 16:42.650
Who sent you?

16:43.690 --> 16:45.140
Our target isn't in the car.

16:45.140 --> 16:46.940
Keep following the GPS tracker.

16:54.130 --> 16:54.990
Officer Jiang.

16:55.750 --> 16:57.150
You've never even met me.

16:57.530 --> 16:59.930
How can you be so confident
that you know me?

17:32.460 --> 17:35.060
[2017]

17:34.640 --> 17:35.490
Jin.

17:35.950 --> 17:37.750
How are things going with Jiang?

17:36.620 --> 17:41.810
[Zhou Jin and Jiang Hansheng's third date]

17:37.990 --> 17:39.990
If it's a good match, settle it soon.

17:40.110 --> 17:43.440
Bring him home and give your dad something
to be happy about.

17:43.710 --> 17:44.800
Robbery!

17:45.140 --> 17:46.180
Run!

17:46.430 --> 17:47.150
Get away!

17:47.150 --> 17:47.990
We're being robbed!

17:47.990 --> 17:48.840
He has a gun!

17:51.910 --> 17:52.510
Freeze!

18:14.650 --> 18:15.310
Don't move!

18:26.240 --> 18:26.870
Zhou Jin!

18:27.160 --> 18:27.690
Zhou Jin!

18:28.390 --> 18:28.910
The gun.

18:29.680 --> 18:30.440
Get him.

18:30.940 --> 18:31.830
It's a replica.

18:31.860 --> 18:32.860
Not a real Type 92.

18:33.610 --> 18:34.250
Arrest...

18:34.860 --> 18:35.710
Arrest him.

18:35.730 --> 18:37.030
He's already under arrest.

18:37.030 --> 18:37.650
Don't worry.

18:37.650 --> 18:38.910
Zhou Jin, are you okay?

18:39.240 --> 18:42.070
Don't tell my parents.

18:42.640 --> 18:43.640
I won't tell them.

18:44.890 --> 18:45.950
Don't fall asleep!

18:46.460 --> 18:47.990
Family members can't go in.

18:48.080 --> 18:48.800
Zhou Jin.

18:55.720 --> 18:58.470
[Operation Room]

19:04.430 --> 19:05.060
Doctor.

19:05.230 --> 19:05.750
Hello.

19:05.780 --> 19:07.760
Let me brief you
on the patient's condition.

19:07.760 --> 19:08.890
She has 3 broken ribs

19:08.930 --> 19:10.130
and a cranial injury.

19:10.200 --> 19:11.930
The surgery carries some risk.

19:12.420 --> 19:13.930
We need a family member's signature.

19:13.930 --> 19:14.660
Is that okay?

19:15.260 --> 19:15.860
I'll sign.

19:15.940 --> 19:16.760
I am a family member.

19:16.760 --> 19:18.140
Okay, here.

19:44.800 --> 19:45.730
I'm done eating.

19:45.860 --> 19:46.590
Are you full?

20:06.950 --> 20:08.010
Let's get married.

20:13.750 --> 20:14.620
Once I'm discharged,

20:14.620 --> 20:16.820
we'll go get our marriage certificate.

20:19.410 --> 20:21.140
Have you thought this through?

20:22.350 --> 20:23.040
Just now.

20:25.650 --> 20:26.580
Jiang Hansheng.

20:28.790 --> 20:29.880
I'm serious.

20:36.190 --> 20:38.390
But we haven't been together that long.

20:38.540 --> 20:40.670
The length of time we've been together

20:40.730 --> 20:42.460
doesn't really mean anything.

20:42.990 --> 20:44.120
I've figured it out.

20:45.570 --> 20:46.900
Life is unpredictable,

20:48.600 --> 20:50.330
so we need to live in the moment.

20:53.190 --> 20:55.320
I trust what I'm feeling right now.

21:02.640 --> 21:03.640
Don't you want to?

21:03.950 --> 21:04.750
Of course I do.

21:07.080 --> 21:08.940
I'm just afraid you'll regret it.

21:09.710 --> 21:10.390
I won't.

21:13.980 --> 21:15.290
What if he comes back for you someday?

21:15.290 --> 21:15.980
He won't.

21:18.670 --> 21:19.310
Okay.

21:20.480 --> 21:21.540
Let's get married.

21:23.390 --> 21:24.360
Don't hurt me.

21:29.110 --> 21:30.110
Don't betray me.

21:34.080 --> 21:34.750
I won't.

21:36.240 --> 21:36.800
Zhou Jin,

21:38.280 --> 21:39.120
I promise you.

21:40.210 --> 21:41.100
I won't hurt you

21:42.040 --> 21:43.110
or betray you.

22:08.010 --> 22:08.540
Zhou Jin.

22:11.510 --> 22:12.380
Do you like me?

22:17.990 --> 22:18.590
It's okay.

22:19.310 --> 22:20.910
No need to answer right away.

22:25.190 --> 22:25.880
Hansheng.

22:48.280 --> 22:48.970
I

22:54.870 --> 22:55.870
trust you.

23:11.150 --> 23:11.910
Come on,

23:11.960 --> 23:12.820
Officer Jiang.

23:14.420 --> 23:15.700
Let's talk about

23:16.240 --> 23:17.220
your girl.

23:31.110 --> 23:32.910
The killer has been shot dead,

23:33.740 --> 23:36.020
but Zhou Chuan's gun is still missing.

23:36.910 --> 23:38.910
The case has to be suspended for now.

23:39.090 --> 23:40.850
For your protection,

23:41.450 --> 23:42.840
once you've recovered,

23:43.320 --> 23:46.850
the organization will arrange
for you to teach at a university.

23:53.840 --> 23:55.950
Protect...

23:56.210 --> 23:57.860
Zhou Jin.

23:59.820 --> 24:03.710
I need to protect Zhou Jin.

24:09.360 --> 24:12.630
[Tomb of the Martyr, Zhou Chuan]

24:17.880 --> 24:18.670
Brother,

24:20.080 --> 24:21.360
I've missed you.

24:43.090 --> 24:43.980
Door unlocked.

24:44.010 --> 24:45.090
Welcome home.

24:48.030 --> 24:51.550
[Zhou Jin, Investigator, Criminal Investigation
Brigade of Haizhou City, Nancheng Branch]

25:58.680 --> 25:59.230
Dan.

25:59.620 --> 26:00.150
Zhou Jin.

26:00.430 --> 26:02.150
The body of a woman was found
downstream of the Tong River.

26:02.150 --> 26:03.060
I'll send you the location.

26:03.060 --> 26:04.260
Get there as soon as possible.

26:04.260 --> 26:04.650
Okay.

26:04.670 --> 26:05.800
I'll be right there.

26:11.430 --> 26:12.040
Door unlocked.

26:12.040 --> 26:13.080
Welcome home.

26:15.740 --> 26:16.200
You're leaving?

26:15.930 --> 26:18.260
[Jiang Hansheng, Associate Professor,
Haizhou University of Political Science and Law]

26:17.230 --> 26:18.660
Just got a call from the team.

26:18.660 --> 26:19.520
There's a case.

26:19.670 --> 26:20.390
It's fine.

26:20.410 --> 26:21.210
I understand.

26:21.360 --> 26:22.750
I'm really sorry.

26:22.750 --> 26:23.910
We had plans today

26:24.040 --> 26:25.770
to set up our new home together.

26:26.670 --> 26:28.270
But that's just how my job is.

26:28.470 --> 26:29.010
It can't be helped.

26:29.010 --> 26:31.540
I have to be ready
for assignments at any time.

26:45.250 --> 26:45.800
Zhou Jin.

26:46.410 --> 26:47.940
Do you like this apartment?

26:49.130 --> 26:49.780
It's nice.

26:52.750 --> 26:53.550
It's very you.

26:54.470 --> 26:54.990
Neat

26:55.710 --> 26:56.370
and serene.

27:01.230 --> 27:02.430
Do you really like it?

27:03.990 --> 27:04.560
I do.

27:06.320 --> 27:07.040
I really need to go now.

27:07.040 --> 27:07.670
I'm running late.

27:07.670 --> 27:08.340
I'll take you.

27:08.340 --> 27:08.800
No need.

27:08.890 --> 27:09.890
I can go by myself.

27:35.980 --> 27:36.560
Move along.

27:36.560 --> 27:37.080
Nothing to see here.

27:37.080 --> 27:38.280
Step back, everyone.

27:48.910 --> 27:49.640
Age:

27:50.080 --> 27:51.290
under 25.

27:51.710 --> 27:52.670
Time of death?

27:52.040 --> 27:54.480
[Lu Pengfei, Investigator,
Nancheng Branch CIB]

27:53.400 --> 27:54.720
About 3 to 4 days ago.

27:54.750 --> 27:55.970
Set up the police tape in front.

27:55.970 --> 27:56.890
Please step back.

27:56.890 --> 27:57.990
We're investigating a case.

27:57.990 --> 27:59.680
Everyone, please move back.

27:59.970 --> 28:00.520
Make way.

28:00.520 --> 28:01.800
No talking.

28:00.540 --> 28:03.710
[Zhao Ping, Investigator,
Nancheng Branch CIB]

28:02.150 --> 28:03.430
Keep quiet.

28:03.560 --> 28:04.150
Senior.

28:05.140 --> 28:05.580
What?

28:05.630 --> 28:06.740
There are too many people here.

28:06.740 --> 28:08.490
Extend the police tape further out.

28:08.490 --> 28:09.620
Zhao Ping, help her.

28:09.620 --> 28:10.420
Be tactful.

28:10.450 --> 28:11.020
Got it.

28:11.640 --> 28:12.550
Let's go, Senior.

28:12.550 --> 28:13.730
Let's set up the police tape.

28:13.730 --> 28:14.190
Come on.

28:15.750 --> 28:16.470
Move along.

28:16.470 --> 28:17.670
Step back, step back.

28:17.710 --> 28:17.990
Here.

28:17.990 --> 28:18.800
Move back, move back.

28:18.800 --> 28:19.520
Please make way.

28:19.520 --> 28:20.360
Step back a bit.

28:20.360 --> 28:21.230
There's nothing to see here.

28:21.230 --> 28:22.430
It'll only upset you.

28:22.770 --> 28:23.640
Back up.

28:24.190 --> 28:25.720
Pull the tape further back.

28:25.750 --> 28:27.060
Everyone should keep an eye out

28:27.060 --> 28:28.390
for any missing persons

28:28.390 --> 28:29.390
or suspicious individuals around you.

28:29.390 --> 28:30.790
Call the police anytime.

28:32.690 --> 28:34.980
I heard the girl died horribly.

28:35.310 --> 28:37.240
Seems like she was shot in the head.

28:37.670 --> 28:39.280
A swimmer found her.

28:39.390 --> 28:41.390
No idea where she drifted from.

28:41.880 --> 28:42.950
Quiet down.

28:43.360 --> 28:45.160
Can we confirm the time of death?

28:45.250 --> 28:46.180
About 3 days ago.

28:46.880 --> 28:48.750
The gunshot wound
is the only fatal injury.

28:48.750 --> 28:49.950
Based on the caliber,

28:50.880 --> 28:51.600
it should be...

28:51.600 --> 28:53.060
Is it from a Type 92 pistol?

28:53.520 --> 28:56.980
Let's wait for the autopsy results
for further confirmation.

28:58.990 --> 29:01.640
The forensic and trace evidence reports
are out.

29:01.640 --> 29:02.640
We can now confirm

29:02.840 --> 29:04.080
it came from Zhou Chuan's gun.

29:03.290 --> 29:07.470
[Tan Shiming, Captain,
Nancheng Branch CIB, Haizhou City]

29:04.770 --> 29:05.530
The 8.17 Case

29:06.510 --> 29:07.440
can now proceed.

29:09.260 --> 29:09.720
Report.

29:11.270 --> 29:11.830
Get out.

29:12.550 --> 29:13.410
Close the door.

29:26.800 --> 29:27.930
Stay 10 meters away.

29:32.920 --> 29:34.010
It won't work.

29:34.530 --> 29:35.970
Zhou Jin isn't suitable.

29:36.600 --> 29:37.190
Besides,

29:37.320 --> 29:38.040
she should recuse herself

29:38.040 --> 29:39.560
from this case.

29:39.930 --> 29:41.780
I'm not assigning her to the 8.17 Case.

29:41.780 --> 29:43.800
I'm assigning her to the
Tong River Corpse Case.

29:43.800 --> 29:45.730
But the murder weapon in that case

29:45.870 --> 29:47.530
is connected to the 8.17 Case.

29:47.600 --> 29:48.830
If you let her investigate,

29:48.830 --> 29:50.430
won't she figure it out soon?

29:50.720 --> 29:52.800
So I believe she'll give it her all.

29:52.970 --> 29:54.430
Yes, she definitely will.

29:54.440 --> 29:55.300
Let me tell you,

29:55.360 --> 29:57.280
just the numbers "8.17" are enough

29:57.280 --> 29:59.340
to make her put in her maximum effort.

30:03.840 --> 30:04.430
Besides,

30:05.470 --> 30:07.040
she just got married.

30:07.430 --> 30:08.750
Why do you have to make her

30:08.750 --> 30:10.600
lead the charge at this time?

30:12.220 --> 30:13.090
She's married?

30:13.990 --> 30:15.040
Just recently.

30:17.640 --> 30:19.500
I agree with everything you said.

30:19.560 --> 30:21.160
But I just have one question.

30:21.720 --> 30:23.240
Is she qualified enough?

30:25.600 --> 30:26.360
Well...

30:26.990 --> 30:28.190
She's young

30:28.840 --> 30:30.100
and lacks experience.

30:30.170 --> 30:32.840
She has never handled
any major cases independently.

30:32.840 --> 30:33.150
So...

30:33.150 --> 30:34.770
No one cares more about solving

30:34.770 --> 30:36.290
the 8.17 Case than her.

30:48.140 --> 30:48.830
Come in.

30:57.120 --> 30:57.710
Sir.

30:58.640 --> 31:00.700
What was all that rush about earlier?

31:03.120 --> 31:04.150
I know.

31:04.910 --> 31:05.880
I'm

31:06.320 --> 31:07.040
young,

31:07.390 --> 31:08.320
inexperienced,

31:08.950 --> 31:10.950
and haven't solved any major cases.

31:14.750 --> 31:16.550
I told you to stay 10 meters away.

31:16.910 --> 31:18.370
Who told you to eavesdrop?

31:18.670 --> 31:19.880
I wasn't eavesdropping.

31:19.880 --> 31:20.730
You weren't?

31:21.080 --> 31:22.340
You said that about me?

31:24.440 --> 31:25.170
No, I didn't.

31:28.270 --> 31:29.960
I want to investigate
the Tong River Corpse Case.

31:29.960 --> 31:30.560
See, see?

31:30.750 --> 31:31.990
You still claim you weren't eavesdropping?

31:31.990 --> 31:33.390
I really wasn't.

31:34.910 --> 31:36.280
I simply believe

31:36.470 --> 31:37.210
that these types of

31:37.210 --> 31:39.190
violent crimes against female victims

31:39.190 --> 31:40.990
are better handled by female officers.

31:40.990 --> 31:42.520
The victim had no ID,

31:42.750 --> 31:44.600
and we couldn't match
any useful information.

31:44.600 --> 31:47.120
We definitely need
more officers for canvassing.

31:47.120 --> 31:48.720
I can certainly contribute.

31:49.040 --> 31:50.640
It's not because of that gun?

31:52.520 --> 31:54.180
Is it really my brother's gun?

31:55.040 --> 31:56.230
No comment.

31:57.880 --> 31:58.560
Sir,

31:58.840 --> 32:00.560
is the 8.17 Case being reopened?

32:00.560 --> 32:02.280
That case was never closed.

32:02.280 --> 32:03.670
There's no reopening to speak of.

32:03.670 --> 32:04.880
You don't need to hide it from me.

32:04.880 --> 32:05.880
It's been 5 years,

32:05.880 --> 32:07.280
and there's been no progress.

32:07.280 --> 32:08.750
It's been a dead end for ages.

32:08.750 --> 32:10.390
What are you snooping around for?

32:10.390 --> 32:11.390
Who told you that?

32:12.750 --> 32:14.210
I don't care how you see me.

32:15.230 --> 32:17.310
I worked my way up
from the security division

32:17.310 --> 32:18.670
just so that someday,

32:19.210 --> 32:21.140
I could solve the 8.17 Case myself.

32:31.600 --> 32:32.120
Fine.

32:34.030 --> 32:35.230
If you're so capable,

32:35.800 --> 32:37.040
go and find out

32:37.290 --> 32:38.350
who this woman was.

32:39.090 --> 32:39.580
Yes.

32:43.080 --> 32:43.720
Sorry for the disturbance.

32:43.720 --> 32:45.120
Thank you for your cooperation.

32:45.120 --> 32:47.390
There are still 31 households
on the east side.

32:47.390 --> 32:48.840
No one has identified the body

32:48.840 --> 32:50.360
and no one has reported a missing person.

32:50.360 --> 32:51.910
This investigation is too difficult.

32:51.910 --> 32:54.150
We don't even know
the victim's identity yet.

32:54.150 --> 32:56.230
Not everyone has someone
who cares about them.

32:56.230 --> 32:58.230
She had neither family nor friends.

32:58.230 --> 32:59.750
Now the only ones who care about her

32:59.750 --> 33:00.750
are us.

33:01.190 --> 33:02.120
Let's continue.

33:02.600 --> 33:04.670
Zhao Ping, your uneven shoulders
are getting worse.

33:04.670 --> 33:05.280
It's fine.

33:06.950 --> 33:07.470
Let's go.

33:07.470 --> 33:09.400
Let's hurry to the next household.

33:09.470 --> 33:09.990
Senior,

33:10.640 --> 33:12.080
your rib injury hasn't fully healed yet.

33:12.080 --> 33:12.810
Take it easy.

33:15.600 --> 33:16.800
The rain is too heavy.

33:18.320 --> 33:19.120
No one's here.

33:19.840 --> 33:21.970
Let's take shelter from the rain here.

33:27.950 --> 33:29.390
This part of the city is too old.

33:29.390 --> 33:30.930
There's not even a single security camera.

33:30.930 --> 33:33.260
I'll report this to the higher-ups later.

33:43.610 --> 33:45.140
What are you doing, Senior?

33:49.750 --> 33:50.350
Zhao Ping.

33:51.710 --> 33:53.310
Isn't this a video doorbell?

33:54.800 --> 33:55.820
Contact the owner.

33:55.820 --> 33:56.270
Okay.

34:06.640 --> 34:08.150
She got out of the taxi

34:08.600 --> 34:10.060
and went toward the river.

34:10.080 --> 34:11.190
These clothes are unmistakable.

34:10.969 --> 34:13.530
[Yu Dan, Investigator,
Nancheng Branch CIB]

34:11.870 --> 34:13.949
But we can only make out
the last 2 digits of the license plate.

34:13.949 --> 34:14.679
The last 2 digits are enough.

34:14.679 --> 34:15.480
I can check it.

34:21.120 --> 34:22.050
Can you check it?

34:38.030 --> 34:39.360
What are you doing here?

34:41.190 --> 34:42.120
Why are you here?

34:43.280 --> 34:44.679
I'm here to find someone.

34:46.610 --> 34:47.409
Find someone?

34:57.710 --> 34:58.920
It's indeed my fault.

34:58.920 --> 34:59.710
I'm sorry.

35:00.010 --> 35:00.960
I forgot to tell you that

35:00.960 --> 35:02.310
I won't be coming home these days.

35:02.310 --> 35:04.310
But you shouldn't come to my workplace.

35:04.310 --> 35:05.480
I was in a meeting.

35:05.850 --> 35:06.910
How embarrassing.

35:08.520 --> 35:10.080
I'm really here to find someone.

35:10.080 --> 35:11.120
Stop kidding.

35:11.670 --> 35:12.480
Who are you looking for?

35:12.480 --> 35:13.000
Senior.

35:14.670 --> 35:15.230
Who is he?

35:18.750 --> 35:19.680
He is...

35:19.700 --> 35:20.700
Professor Jiang.

35:21.950 --> 35:23.580
You're Professor Jiang, right?

35:23.580 --> 35:24.180
Chief Tan.

35:24.640 --> 35:25.450
Hello.

35:25.640 --> 35:26.600
Welcome.

35:26.970 --> 35:27.640
It's great

35:27.670 --> 35:28.800
that you could come.

35:28.990 --> 35:29.520
Please.

35:32.740 --> 35:33.470
Colleagues.

35:36.270 --> 35:37.470
Let me introduce you.

35:38.750 --> 35:39.680
Jiang Hansheng,

35:39.830 --> 35:40.780
Professor Jiang,

35:40.780 --> 35:42.850
is our criminal profiling expert

35:42.890 --> 35:45.170
and Director Wang Pengze's star student.

35:45.170 --> 35:46.100
Professor Jiang

35:46.270 --> 35:47.400
started his career

35:47.550 --> 35:48.460
at the Provincial Department

35:48.460 --> 35:49.540
in the

35:49.790 --> 35:51.120
Crime Research Office.

35:51.270 --> 35:52.190
Currently,

35:52.310 --> 35:53.670
he's working at the Haizhou University
of Political Science and Law

35:53.670 --> 35:54.450
as a professor.

35:54.450 --> 35:56.900
This time,
he's joining us as an external expert

35:56.900 --> 35:58.530
to assist with our precinct's work.

35:58.530 --> 36:00.960
Let's give him a warm welcome.

36:05.520 --> 36:07.380
I'm just an Associate Professor.

36:08.560 --> 36:10.200
Being an Associate Professor is great!

36:10.200 --> 36:11.970
That means you're young.

36:12.990 --> 36:13.810
Come.

36:13.830 --> 36:15.960
Welcome, Associate Professor Jiang.

36:18.560 --> 36:20.090
Continue your discussion.

36:20.980 --> 36:21.940
Associate Professor Jiang,

36:21.940 --> 36:23.270
let's talk in my office.

36:25.580 --> 36:26.240
Wait for me.

36:30.380 --> 36:31.250
Sir.

36:33.670 --> 36:34.600
He's quite good.

36:40.850 --> 36:42.200
He really is good.

36:42.610 --> 36:43.770
What's so good about him?

36:43.770 --> 36:44.700
He's so intense.

36:44.800 --> 36:45.750
Senior, let me tell you.

36:45.750 --> 36:46.760
The way he looked at you wasn't normal.

36:46.760 --> 36:47.480
Who is he?

36:47.630 --> 36:48.520
Didn't they just say?

36:48.050 --> 36:51.490
[Liu Liang, Investigator, Criminal
Investigation Brigade of Nancheng Branch]

36:48.550 --> 36:49.640
He's Professor Jiang Hansheng.

36:49.640 --> 36:50.370
You know him?

36:50.520 --> 36:51.740
Is that what he was asking?

36:51.740 --> 36:53.670
And you call yourself a detective.

36:54.180 --> 36:54.870
Zhou.

36:56.150 --> 36:57.150
Tell us the truth.

36:57.630 --> 36:58.920
Yes, what's going on?

36:59.120 --> 37:00.000
What's happening?

37:00.000 --> 37:01.120
Senior, tell us about it.

37:01.120 --> 37:01.480
I...

37:01.480 --> 37:02.480
Who is he?

37:02.750 --> 37:03.480
Oh, give it a rest.

37:03.480 --> 37:04.230
You talk too much.

37:04.230 --> 37:04.790
No, he...

37:04.790 --> 37:05.830
Found it!

37:06.640 --> 37:09.040
[Bai Yang, Technician, Criminal
Investigation Brigade of Nancheng Branch]

37:09.390 --> 37:13.900
[Shangyue Hotel]

37:16.650 --> 37:18.860
[Wan Chongshan, Investigator, Criminal
Investigation Brigade of Nancheng Branch]

37:22.510 --> 37:23.300
Same car,

37:23.520 --> 37:24.640
same physical characteristics,

37:24.640 --> 37:25.770
and the same outfit.

37:25.870 --> 37:26.870
The time was

37:26.890 --> 37:27.890
July 23rd, night,

37:28.020 --> 37:29.050
10:57 PM.

37:29.080 --> 37:31.250
The time of death was
early morning on the 24th.

37:31.250 --> 37:32.720
This means for some reason,

37:32.720 --> 37:34.600
she left the hotel late at night,

37:34.600 --> 37:36.640
took a car to the Tong River riverbank,

37:36.640 --> 37:37.720
and was shot to death.

37:37.720 --> 37:39.000
After being killed, her body was dumped

37:39.000 --> 37:39.600
and carried downstream.

37:39.600 --> 37:40.750
Then, on July 27th,

37:41.600 --> 37:43.060
a swimmer discovered her.

37:43.560 --> 37:44.350
That guy was so scared that

37:44.350 --> 37:45.950
he still can't get out of bed.

37:49.360 --> 37:51.840
[Shangyue Hotel]

38:31.660 --> 38:32.660
Jiang Hansheng.

38:41.190 --> 38:42.190
Professor Jiang.

38:48.260 --> 38:50.520
It's the gun from the 8.17 Case, isn't it?

38:54.150 --> 38:55.120
Director Lu said

38:55.890 --> 38:57.750
you'd understand once you saw it.

38:58.360 --> 38:59.150
He was right.

39:00.290 --> 39:02.090
Is Zhou Jin working on this case?

39:02.190 --> 39:05.050
She's now responsible for
identifying the victim.

39:11.740 --> 39:13.830
If I don't go, I won't feel at ease.

39:14.330 --> 39:15.660
Your senior is on one side,

39:15.660 --> 39:17.140
and Mr. Wan is on the other.

39:17.310 --> 39:18.600
What are you worried about?

39:18.600 --> 39:20.060
Just take me to one of them.

39:21.480 --> 39:22.190
No way.

39:22.600 --> 39:24.200
Your injury has just healed.

39:24.380 --> 39:25.870
At this rate, you'll end up like me.

39:25.870 --> 39:27.000
I injured my back years ago,

39:27.000 --> 39:28.920
and it still hurts whenever it rains.

39:28.920 --> 39:31.440
Don't take your youth for granted.

39:32.040 --> 39:33.330
It takes 100 days to recover
from bone injuries.

39:33.330 --> 39:34.960
Can we continue
after you've fully recovered?

39:34.960 --> 39:35.810
Stop arguing with me.

39:35.810 --> 39:37.040
Focus on getting well.

39:37.040 --> 39:37.620
That's what matters most.

39:37.620 --> 39:38.150
Zhou Jin.

39:51.120 --> 39:51.680
Hello.

39:53.150 --> 39:54.550
Hello, Professor Jiang.

39:59.010 --> 39:59.870
This is my wife.

40:05.830 --> 40:07.090
What a perfect couple!

40:07.140 --> 40:09.580
Zhou Jin and Professor Jiang are married.

40:09.830 --> 40:11.150
I'm aware of that.

40:12.010 --> 40:13.070
That's wonderful.

40:13.120 --> 40:13.580
Indeed.

40:13.650 --> 40:14.310
Good.

40:14.310 --> 40:15.020
I need to get back to work.

40:15.020 --> 40:16.540
It's my bad.

40:16.570 --> 40:17.490
Everyone's been so busy lately,

40:17.490 --> 40:19.490
I didn't have time to break the news.

40:20.470 --> 40:23.030
Our marriage was also quite sudden.

40:23.280 --> 40:26.120
How could something
as important as marriage be so sudden?

40:26.120 --> 40:27.850
You could have at least told us.

40:28.670 --> 40:29.870
It was indeed sudden.

40:30.820 --> 40:31.410
Sir.

40:31.770 --> 40:33.500
Can I also go to Shangyue Hotel?

40:33.730 --> 40:35.990
I want to confirm the victim's identity.

40:36.920 --> 40:37.400
Well...

40:37.450 --> 40:38.050
Chief Tan.

40:38.640 --> 40:39.770
Can I accompany her?

40:40.440 --> 40:41.440
Of course you can.

40:41.830 --> 40:42.830
I got you this badge

40:42.830 --> 40:44.270
to help you with the investigation.

40:44.270 --> 40:44.800
However,

40:45.000 --> 40:46.150
we'll have to trouble you

40:46.150 --> 40:47.010
with this trip.

40:48.830 --> 40:49.360
Zhou Jin.

40:50.230 --> 40:51.440
I'd like a private word with you

40:51.440 --> 40:52.480
about this case.

40:53.440 --> 40:53.920
Sure.

40:56.520 --> 40:58.040
What were you talking about just now?

40:58.040 --> 41:00.300
Does Chief Tan have instructions for me?

41:04.000 --> 41:05.060
It's not Chief Tan.

41:05.160 --> 41:05.680
It's me.

41:06.720 --> 41:07.270
Zhou Jin.

41:07.800 --> 41:09.230
You have no experience confronting

41:09.230 --> 41:10.750
the people behind the 8.17 Case.

41:10.750 --> 41:11.920
Their past actions

41:12.180 --> 41:14.690
prove they have strong
provocative tendencies.

41:14.690 --> 41:15.930
When provocation fails,

41:15.930 --> 41:16.970
revenge follows.

41:17.750 --> 41:19.150
New leads are good,

41:19.810 --> 41:21.410
but we must remain vigilant.

41:21.460 --> 41:22.260
I understand.

41:23.160 --> 41:23.990
That group of people

41:23.990 --> 41:26.190
has no respect for the police or the law.

41:27.000 --> 41:29.460
That's why my brother
suffered so terribly.

41:30.350 --> 41:31.150
Get in the car.

41:39.750 --> 41:41.080
I haven't asked you yet.

41:41.670 --> 41:42.730
What exactly do you

41:42.960 --> 41:43.960
teach at school?

41:45.320 --> 41:46.050
Psychology.

41:46.520 --> 41:48.180
Specifically, which branch?

41:49.310 --> 41:50.310
Don't tell me it's

41:50.780 --> 41:52.040
criminal psychology?

41:52.400 --> 41:52.870
It is.

41:54.340 --> 41:56.220
I was afraid you wouldn't
want to work with someone

41:56.220 --> 41:58.350
in the same field, so I didn't tell you.

41:58.790 --> 41:59.390
It's fine.

41:59.800 --> 42:00.960
You're not on the front line,

42:00.960 --> 42:02.890
so I guess you're half a colleague.

42:04.250 --> 42:05.420
But you never told me

42:05.850 --> 42:08.120
that you worked
at the provincial department before.

42:08.120 --> 42:09.920
What else are you hiding from me?

42:10.690 --> 42:11.870
Back then, your family and the matchmaker

42:11.870 --> 42:13.330
had several requirements

42:13.400 --> 42:14.860
that I didn't really meet.

42:15.330 --> 42:15.930
Like what?

42:17.190 --> 42:18.040
Having both parents alive,

42:18.040 --> 42:19.240
a harmonious family,

42:19.310 --> 42:20.640
and a nine-to-five job.

42:21.370 --> 42:22.310
What kind of requirements are those?

42:22.310 --> 42:22.910
It's okay.

42:23.600 --> 42:25.660
I'll keep covering for you with them.

42:26.270 --> 42:26.870
So,

42:27.450 --> 42:28.530
what do you expect

42:28.750 --> 42:29.730
from a partner?

42:35.710 --> 42:36.310
Zhou Jin,

42:38.150 --> 42:39.880
I hope you won't get hurt again.

42:48.430 --> 42:49.230
In the future,

42:49.400 --> 42:51.130
I'll definitely face dangers.

42:51.960 --> 42:53.800
But the more dangerous a place is,

42:53.800 --> 42:56.000
the greater the opportunity it offers.

42:56.070 --> 42:57.730
Don't worry, Jiang Hansheng.

42:58.000 --> 42:59.270
I'll definitely take good care of myself.
